</h1>

<div class="entry-meta">
<span class="date"><a href="http://lex.pwsztar.edu.pl/?p=962" title="Permalink to polsko-niemieckie seminarium prawa podatkowego" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2016-10-01T18:50:10+00:00">01/10/2016</time></a></span><span class="categories-links"><a href="http://lex.pwsztar.edu.pl/?cat=1" rel="category">Uncategorized</a></span><span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://lex.pwsztar.edu.pl/?author=1" title="View all posts by lex" rel="author">lex</a></span>					</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
